            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, goodness. We went all the way there, but came home tired and empty-handed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x129,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, so that ruin had that kind of tra‐uh, treasures?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x12b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "The owner and I had no idea.<CR>You guys are pretty good."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "But if we can't carry them out,<CR>I feel like there's no point."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I get the feeling that the owner would somehow widen the entrance to get them out..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "But who knows how much money that'll take? It seems like a lot of work..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "So, please keep this a secret from the Owner."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "We know. If it's such a huge construction project, we probably won't be needed, anyways."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* This was the only thing I was able to bring back."
